                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-lucide="store" aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-store w-5 h-5 text-purple-600"><path d="M15 21v-5a1 1 0 0 0-1-1h-4a1 1 0 0 0-1 1v5"></path><path d="M17.774 10.31a1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.549 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.451 0 1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.548 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.452 0 1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.549 0 2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.77-3.248l2.889-4.184A2 2 0 0 1 7 2h10a2 2 0 0 1 1.653.873l2.895 4.192a2.5 2.5 0 0 1-3.774 3.244"></path><path d="M4 10.95V19a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-8.05"></path></svg>
                                Lojas Participantes do Projeto
                            </h2>
                            
                            <div class="flex items-center bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-lg px-3 shadow-sm focus-within:border-blue-500 transition-colors w-full md:w-auto">
                                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" data-lucide="search" aria-hidden="true" class="lucide lucide-search w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"><path d="m21 21-4.34-4.34"></path><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"></circle></svg>
                                <input id="filterGE" type="text" oninput="updateFilter('ge', this.value)" value="" placeholder="Filtrar por G.E..." class="text-sm bg-transparent border-none outline-none py-2 pl-2 w-full sm:w-48 text-slate-600 placeholder-slate-400">
                            </div>
